    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type of plastic characterized by resistance to aggressive environments, including extremes of weather, and temperatures ranging from near 0 to 260 degrees Celsius.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
